Assignment Details : Using a reed switch in the circuit, make a physical model that has led and/or buzzer

Ideation : Similar to OT doors, that have 2 different lights depending on the state of the door.
Door Open - Green (OT is open)
Door Closed - Red (Operation in progress)

So, the door is a magnet, 2 reed switches on either side for the light/buzzer to switch on
